  "headline20": "Critical operational constraints are flagged at 5 airports right now.",
  "management45": "Critical operational constraints are flagged at 5 airports right now. No engine anti-ice operations are currently flagged. Across base airports: 1 critical, 10 high, 9 medium, 19 normal. Key bases needing attention include Chişinău (RMO/LUKK), Bucharest Henri Coandă (OTP/LROP) and Craiova (CRA/LRCV); plus 8 other bases. 9 additional base airports are at medium severity and should be monitored closely. At base airports, the dominant pattern is mist, low cloud base and fog / freezing fog  — most notably around Venice Marco Polo (VCE/LIPZ), Suceava Stefan cel Mare (SCV/LRSV) and Craiova (CRA/LRCV). Network hotspots: Turku (TKU/EFTU), Oslo-Gardermoen (OSL/ENGM), Sandefjord Airport, Torp (TRF/ENTO), Venice Marco Polo (VCE/LIPZ), Shirak (LWN/UDSG). Primary drivers: very low visibility, low cloud base and fog / freezing fog. Expected impact is reduced runway capacity with higher delay and diversion risk, especially where visibility/RVR and cloud base are very low. Since the last update, 2 airports changed status, led by Lennart Meri Tallinn (TLL/EETN), Eindhoven (EIN/EHEH).",
  "detail90": "Critical operational constraints are flagged at 5 airports right now. Base airports (focus): Chişinău (RMO/LUKK) — HIGH: freezing fog; cold-temperature performance penalties; visibility down to 600 m, cloud base around 200 ft | Bucharest Henri Coandă (OTP/LROP) — HIGH: mist; cold-temperature performance penalties; visibility down to 1.5 km, cloud base around 200 ft | Craiova (CRA/LRCV) — HIGH: freezing fog; cold-temperature performance penalties; visibility down to 200 m, RVR down to 325 m, cloud base around 100 ft | Vilnius (VNO/EYVI) — HIGH: freezing fog; visibility down to 500 m, cloud base around 200 ft | Kraków John Paul II (KRK/EPKK) — HIGH: freezing fog; visibility down to 500 m; forecast below approach minima at times | Venice Marco Polo (VCE/LIPZ) — CRIT: fog; visibility down to 100 m, cloud base around 100 ft and 5 others. Worst affected now: Turku (TKU/EFTU) — CRIT: fog; snow; visibility down to 700 m, cloud base around 100 ft (drivers: runway visual range (RVR) constraints, approach minima limits, very low visibility) | Oslo-Gardermoen (OSL/ENGM) — CRIT: freezing fog; snow; cold-temperature performance penalties (drivers: low-visibility procedures (reduced capacity), runway visual range (RVR) constraints, cold-temperature performance penalties) | Sandefjord Airport, Torp (TRF/ENTO) — CRIT: freezing fog; snow; cold-temperature performance penalties (drivers: low-visibility procedures (reduced capacity), runway visual range (RVR) constraints, approach minima limits) | Venice Marco Polo (VCE/LIPZ) — CRIT: fog; visibility down to 100 m, cloud base around 100 ft (drivers: low-visibility procedures (reduced capacity), runway visual range (RVR) constraints, approach minima limits) | Shirak (LWN/UDSG) — CRIT: freezing fog; snow; cold-temperature performance penalties (drivers: approach minima limits, cold-temperature performance penalties, very low visibility). Changed since last run: Lennart Meri Tallinn (TLL/EETN), Eindhoven (EIN/EHEH).",
